			  <h3 class="block-title">Information about the site owner</h3>

              <p>Belarussian National Bar Association brings together regional and Minsk City Bar Association. National Bar Association was founded in 1997 and operates under the Charter. The new edition of the Charter approved by the Board May 3, 2012. </p>
              <p>National Bar Association represents and protects the interests of the lawyers in their relations with public authorities in other organizations and coordinates the activities of the territorial bar associations, implement measures aimed at improving the quality of legal aid.</p>
